event_text: As a storm rages across the mountain outside, m_c is tucked up in the medicine cat den, their sleep anything but restful. They keep seeing flashes of prophecy_list_sight. They wake with a shiver, wondering what their dreams mean for the Clan.
The things they saw today, omen_list_sight... m_c sits on an isolated mountain ledge, considering what the omens foretell.

Through the long, cold night, m_c brings the young cats of the Clan with them down the tunnels. Their words paint an enchanting picture of the ancestors of o_c as they point out the red pawprints of long dead heroes and villains, telling the Clan's triumphs and failures.
